sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Handler
    participant Orchestrator as EnhancedPdfOrchestrator
    participant Unstructured as Unstructured.py
    participant SmolDocling
    participant Docnet
    participant Domain as PdfDocument
    participant DB as Database
    participant Events

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/ingest/pdf/{pdfId}/extract

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(ExtractPdfTextCommand)

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>DB: Get PdfDocument
    DB-->>Handler: PdfDocument (Status: Pending)

    Handler->>Domain: StartProcessing()
    Domain->>Domain: Status = Extracting

    Handler->>Orchestrator: ExecutePipeline(pdfId)

    Note over Orchestrator: STAGE 1: Unstructured.py
    Orchestrator->>Unstructured: POST /extract
    Unstructured->>Unstructured: hi_res layout analysis
    Unstructured-->>Orchestrator: {text, quality: 0.87}

    Orchestrator->>Orchestrator: Calculate quality score
    Note over Orchestrator: Quality 0.87 ≥ 0.80 ✓

    Orchestrator->>Domain: RecordAttempt("Unstructured", 0.87, true)
    Orchestrator->>Domain: MarkCompleted(text, 0.87)
    Domain->>Domain: Status = Completed
    Domain->>Domain: ExtractedText = result
    Domain->>Domain: QualityScore = 0.87
    Domain->>Events: Raise PdfExtractedEvent

    alt Quality < 0.80 (Fallback to Stage 2)
        Note over Orchestrator: STAGE 2: SmolDocling VLM
        Orchestrator->>SmolDocling: POST /extract
        SmolDocling->>SmolDocling: Vision-language processing
        SmolDocling-->>Orchestrator: {text, quality: 0.72}

        Orchestrator->>Domain: RecordAttempt("SmolDocling", 0.72, true)

        alt Quality < 0.70 (Fallback to Stage 3)
            Note over Orchestrator: STAGE 3: Docnet OCR
            Orchestrator->>Docnet: POST /extract
            Docnet->>Docnet: OCR fallback
            Docnet-->>Orchestrator: {text, quality: 0.55}
            Orchestrator->>Domain: RecordAttempt("Docnet", 0.55, true)
        end
    end

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(document)
    DB-->>Handler: Document saved ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish PdfExtractedEvent

    Handler-->>Mediator: ExtractionResult
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: ExtractionResult

    Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK
    Note left of Client: {success, qualityScore, stageUsed}
